al. However this game release this month (February) and not in March so you have to consider that maybe the reason why so pricey.Random Question: I have a friend who bought this game and they are having problems with Framerate drops and such any ideas why?Me: I had similar problems with my game after I installed it and I have an Nvidia graphics card. I even went into my Nivida control panel settings to make sure all my games were using the Nivida card and not the standard video card and still I was experience framerate drops. So I just rebooted my pc so the game is in sync with the video card driver hope this helps.Random Question: No he tried all of that....Me: Well..... He better hope 2K patches the game up because that is mostly the reason.------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*2K Games please focus on hiring voice actors for MyCareer mode and Universe mode because the promo system is a good idea but it's useless and boring after awhile reading all the $hit. Showcase mode should NOT be in the base game you should only include that mode as a DLC or integrate Showcase mode in Universe mode because we could careless about the replay value because that mode doesn't have any unless your really bored and don't have online......
