he matches that you like and this is sort of like a never ending story mode. There are promos to make any wrestler a Face or Heel too.-Heard online multiplayer has flaws, but I haven't tried it nor want to play it online. Great for couch coop with friends. Also other reviews here say the game crashes a lot, but hasn't occured to me even once yet maybe because my pc is good. i7 4790k @4 ghz, 16gb ram and gtx 970.-Overall, if you own 2k16 this doesn't change too much, with less story related content, but packs a bunch of improvements and extra features in the details that 2k16 lacks. So for those looking for local coop, this should be great, especially if you own an ultrawide monitor."
